quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  15,16,"Ampa sε, Yayε nsoromma (akεseε) wͻ soro, εna Yama ayε fε ama wͻn a wͻhwε."
  15,17,"Ɛna Yεbͻ ho ban fri ͻbonsam biara a yato no atwene (anaasε yapo no no nsam)."
  15,18,"Na mmom obia obewia (neho akͻ) tie no deε ogya frama pefee bedi n’akyi."
  15,19,"Asaase nso Yatrε mu εna Yεde mmepͻ a esisi hͻ pintinn asisi soͻ, εna Yε’ma nneεma ahodoͻ pii a εyε dε fifiri wͻ soͻ."
  15,20,"Ɛna Yayε deε ehia wͻ asetena mu ama mo, ne wͻn nso a εnyε mo na mobͻ wͻn akͻnhoma."
  15,21,"Biribiara ho akoradeε wͻ Yεn hͻ, na Yɛsiane no wͻ nhyehyεε a yenim so."
  15,22,"Ɛna Yɛsoma mframa a εkayan (mununkum), na Yasiane nsuo afri soro de ama mo anom aberε a εnyε mo na mokoraa (nsuo) no."
  15,23,"Nokorε sε, Yεn na yεma nkwa εna Yekum, na Yεn na (sε mowu kͻ a, Ye’si mo anan mu) di adeε."
  15,24,"Nokorε sε Yenim momu (awoͻ ntotoa soͻ) a wͻdii kan no, εna ampa nso sε Yenim wͻn a wͻdi akyire no."
  15,25,"Nokorε sε, wo Wura Nyankopͻn, Ͻno na Ɔbεboa wͻn (nyinaa) ano (wͻ Atemmuda). Nokorε sε, Ɔne Onyansafoͻ, Ɔne Onimdefoͻ."
  15,26,"Nokorε sε, Yεbͻͻ onipa fri nεteε a awoͻ a εnee wͻ mu a efri atεkyε a yanwene mu."
  15,27,"Ɛna Jinn no nso Yedii kan bͻͻ no fri ogya kεterεma mu (ansa na yεrebͻ onipa)."
  15,28,"Kae εberε a wo Wura Nyankopͻn ka kyerεε Soro abͻfoͻ no sε: “Merebεbͻ onipa afri nεteε a awoͻ a εnee wͻ mu a efri atεkyε a yanwene mu”."
  15,29,"“Enti sε Menwene no pεpεεpε wie na Mehome Mehonhom gu ne mu a, monfa moho nkͻ fͻm na monfa moanim mmutu fͻm ma no."
  15,30,"Enti Soro abͻfoͻ no nyinaa bͻͻ mu de wͻn anim butuu fͻm (brεε wͻn ho ase) maa (Adam)."
  15,31,"Gyesε Ibliis, wampene sε ͻbεka wͻn a wͻde wͻn anim butuu fͻm (brεε wͻn ho aseε) no ho."
